and try a new concept

298
00:15:54.745 --> 00:15:56.580
that lived within that existing brand

299
00:15:56.664 --> 00:15:58.582
and then spin it out if it was successful.

300
00:15:58.666 --> 00:16:01.043
or he would acquire
a brand that was failing.

301
00:16:02.878 --> 00:16:05.881
[Rupp] <i>Abercrombie already had</i>
