<i>the windows of the store</i>

305
00:16:18.352 --> 00:16:20.771
<i>as being kind of the masculine dream.</i>

306
00:16:22.106 --> 00:16:25.234
[Maheshwari] <i>And it catered</i>
<i>to sort of elite sportsmen.</i>

307
00:16:25.818 --> 00:16:28.570
