-[dog whimpers]

344
00:18:35.781 --> 00:18:39.368
The Abercrombie college kid drives a Jeep.

345
00:18:39.451 --> 00:18:41.912
-[engine revs]
-And he doesn't drive the sedan.

346
00:18:42.579 --> 00:18:43.789
[horn beeps]

347
00:18:45.290 --> 00:18:47.876
Fashion is an industry that is notorious

348
00:18:47.960 --> 00:18:50.546
