the impact that Bruce Weber…

414
00:22:42.819 --> 00:22:44.946
his aesthetic had.

415
00:22:45.030 --> 00:22:48.450
I mean.
Mike put all his eggs in that basket.

416
00:22:50.285 --> 00:22:53.538
The Abercrombie aesthetic
